<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Booking Street</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2196F3;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #2196F3;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Booking Street!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      
      <p>Welcome to Booking Street! We're excited to have you join our community of service users. Your account has been successfully created with the email address: <strong>{{email}}</strong></p>

      <p>With Booking Street, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Book professional services with ease</li>
        <li>Track your bookings in real-time</li>
        <li>Connect with verified service providers</li>
        <li>Manage your appointments efficiently</li>
      </ul>


      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The Booking Street Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you didn't create a Booking Street account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>